                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '1') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

[2023/05/01 04:51:38] SQL Query: SELECT 
                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '2') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '2') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '2') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category

                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

[2023/05/03 08:17:37] SQL Query: SELECT 
                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '1') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '2') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '1') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

            FROM

                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '2') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

[2023/05/09 07:57:25] SQL Query: SELECT * FROM img_product WHERE product_id = '2'
[2023/05/09 07:57:25] SQL Query: SELECT 
                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '2') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category

[2023/05/11 07:37:52] SQL Query: SELECT 
                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '5') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category

[2023/05/11 09:51:34] SQL Query: SELECT * FROM img_product WHERE product_id = '8'
[2023/05/11 09:51:34] SQL Query: SELECT 
                c1.name_category AS category1, c1.url AS url1,
                c2.name_category AS category2, c2.url AS url2,
                c3.name_category AS category3, c3.url AS url3
            FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM products WHERE id_product = '8') p
                JOIN categories c1 ON p.category_id = c1.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c2 ON c1.fatherCategory = c2.id_category
                LEFT JOIN categories c3 ON c2.fatherCategory = c3.id_category
